    "As FedFM continue to evolve, the focus on training and aggregation methodologies, trustworthiness measures, incentive mechanisms, and participant management strategies will be crucial for its success.",
    "This field is essential for unlocking the full potential of FMs by enabling efficient and trustworthy access to privately owned valuable data via FL.",
